Update Service Categories table to use AG-Grid (#7880)

* update integration tests Service Categories
pull_request_title: Update Service Categories table to use AG-Grid
pull_request_body:
Closes: #6498 
This updates the "Service Categories" Traffic Portal page to use AG-Grid instead of JQuery datatables.
<hr/>

## Which Traffic Control components are affected by this PR?
- Traffic Portal

## What is the best way to verify this PR?
Make sure all the TP tests pass, and make sure the new table looks okay.
